001package gust.backend.transport;
002
003import com.google.api.gax.core.CredentialsProvider;
004
005import javax.annotation.Nonnull;
006import java.util.List;
007import java.util.Optional;
008
009
010/**
011 * Transport-layer credentials configuration for use with managed gRPC connections. Specifies a credential provider for
012 * use with auto-initialized and pooled RPC channels.
013 */
014public interface GrpcTransportCredentials extends TransportCredentials {
015  /**
016   * @return Credentials provider that should be active for managed RPC channel calls, with an empty set of scopes.
017   */
018  default @Nonnull Optional<CredentialsProvider> credentialsProvider() {
019    return credentialsProvider(Optional.empty());
020  }
021
022  /**
023   * @return Credentials provider that should be active for managed RPC channel calls.
024   */
025  default @Nonnull Optional<CredentialsProvider> credentialsProvider(@Nonnull Optional<List<String>> scopes) {
026    return Optional.empty();
027  }
028}
